16:10.803 --> 16:13.389
{\an3}I mean, there were a series
of men that I had to call "dad,"

16:13.472 --> 16:15.891
but back to you, Your Honor.

16:15.974 --> 16:17.851
Wow, that must have been hard.

16:17.935 --> 16:20.062
