Wait, wait, wait, wait,

18:02.706 --> 18:06.210
"Victoria Chase and Dane Stevens
are a revelation.

18:06.293 --> 18:09.004
{\an3}Their decision
not to kiss was genius."

18:09.087 --> 18:10.172
{\an3}We did it!

18:10.255 --> 18:13.467
{\an1}Of course we did.
